results.title: Live Well Laugh Often Love Much Home Wall Decal, Home Decor Wall Graphic, Wall Art
results.description:
We want to help you add the finishing touches to your home decorating with our scripture and inspirational wall decals. These decals are easy to install with our step by step instructions, and look as though you painted it on your wall! We want to help your room look finished and put together as easy as possible, and better yet the graphics with instructions and a practice graphic get delivered to your front door. Not the scripture or quote you want? Don't worry we love custom orders!
Here is a link to our custom order items:

Here is a link to more already designed decals for your home:

Live Well Laugh Often Love Much

Our graphics are made with matte Oracal indoor wall vinyl. This material can be applied to a smooth clean surface. Rough or highly textured walls will be hard to install.

Matte vinyl makes graphics look like your graphics were painted on the wall, but can be easily removed at a later date.

Visit our website for installation directions:
http://www.signguysandgal.com/vinyl_install_tips
*graphics will come with installation tips, practice graphic and squeegee for installation

Graphics will be shipped within 3 business days (Mon.-Fri) of received payment.

Put color choice in Message to Seller box. If no color is requested your graphic will be made in black.


*Convo us for custom wall graphics.
*Convo us for custom sizes.
*Convo us for outdoor/high performance/gloss vinyl graphics.

Want To See More? Visit my shop https://etsy.me/2ECYApn

results.title: Embroidered Irish Claddagh Towel | St. Patrick's Day Decor | Custom Embroidery | Irish Wedding Gift | Wedding Shower Gift | Irish Kitchen
results.description:
Adorable Irish custom embroidered towels - with the classic Irish Claddagh. Are you or is someone you love Irish and love to show that in their kitchen? This is a great addition to a gift for that perfect couple! These towels are sure to get you and your guests smiling! Perfect for your kitchen, bathroom, coffee bar, or beverage bar! 

Do you want to add customization? Add a last name or couple name for just $5 more! Pick this option in the order section and enter the customization details in the personalization section. 

The towels used will be 16 inches x 26 inches and with terry cloth. We do have tea towels as options as well, if you prefer a tea towel (white with stripes on the side of a solid color) pick the tea towel option in the options. Choose your towel color / type you'd like in the options here.

I will message you after the order is placed to make sure we are on the same page for towel order, colors, etc. If you have specific request such as thread color or a custom request, notate that in the personalization box here.

The towels will be completed and mailed within 3 business days.

If you have any questions at all, let me know!
